original_title: Manfred Mann - Music Night Live in Switzerland 2006
overview: Manfred Mann's Earth Band perform live at the Rock Sound Festival in Huttwil, Switzerland on July 8th, 2006. TV Recording broadcast recorded on Pro-Shot SF 2 in 2007. Tracklist includes: 1. Don't Kill It Carol, 2. Demolition Man, 3. Blinded By The Light, 4. Davy's On The Road Again, 5. the Mighty Quinn
title: Manfred Mann - Music Night Live in Switzerland 2006
